snippet.title: Almost my floor -  announcement trailer (point&click horror adventure)
snippet.description:
Steam link - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1298080/Almost_My_Floor/
Almost my floor - classic point&click adventure in horror atmosphere. Alex (main character) is a simple man who lives common live. But one day everything will change. Is he actually so simple?
